#: ../../intro.rst:6
msgid ""
"There are plenty of 'scripts' and websites available for performing DSMR "
"readings. This project however is a full stack solution. This allows a "
"decent implementation of most features, but requires a certain 'skill' as"
" you will need to install several dependencies."
msgstr ""

